    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA53-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu varaivu nīṭṭippat tōḻi ciṟaippuṟamākac colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what the confidante said while [HE] was behind the fence when he was delaying marriage.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA53">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            yāṉaḵ tañciṉeṉ karappavun tāṉaḵ</l>
<l>            taṟintaṉaḷ kollō varuḷiṉaḷ kollō</l>
<l>            vevaṉko ṟōḻi yaṉṉai kaṇṇiyatu</l>
<l>            vāṉuṟa nivanta perumalaik kavāaṉ</l>
<l>            ṉārkali vāṉan talaii naṭunāṭ </l>
<l>            kaṉaipeyal poḻinteṉak kāṉak kalyāṟṟu</l>
<l>            muḷiyilai kaḻittaṉa mukiḻiṇar malaroṭu</l>
<l>            varuviruntiṟ ṟīnīr maruntu mākun</l>
<l>            taṇṇeṉa vuṇṭu kaṇṇi ṉōkki</l>
<l>            muṉiyā tāṭa peṟiṉivaḷ </l>
<l>            paṉiyun tīrkuvaḷ celkeṉ ṟōḷē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>I was afraid of that, even though I hid [it]:</l>
<l rend="indent4">has she herself</l>
<l rend="indent2">understood it? Is she considerate?</l>
<l>What is the thing mother has seen,</l>
<l rend="indent"> who said:</l>
<l rend="indent3">“she may go, ending any fever,</l>
<l rend="indent3">if she could play [in there] without disgust,</l>
<l rend="indent3">seeing with [her] eyes: it is cool,<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">kaṇṇiṉ nōkki</term> seems to have taken here the function of an embedding construction: the <term xml:lang="ta">uṇṭu</term> sentence can only be interpreted as the object of looking.</note></l>
<l rend="indent">when water sweet as a coming feast is a remedy too,</l>
<l rend="indent"> with flowers [and] bud clusters that have removed the dry leaves</l>
<l rend="indent2">in the stony river in the forest, because intense rain has flown</l>
<l rend="indent3">at midnight, being offered from a fully bustling sky</l>
<l rend="indent3">on the slope of the big mountain come up to reach the sky.”<note place="foot">How to account for syntax here?</note></l>
        </lg>
         </div>
